column16: Kya mein yeh tasweer daikh sakti hoon?
Yaqinan! Yeh mairay khandan ki tasweer hai.
Nae, yeh mairay dada hain! Aur yeh mairi dadi hain.
Haan woh lagtay hain! Aur yeh mairi phupho aur chacha hain.
Yeh maira chota bhai hai. Mairi aik behan bhi hai.
Kya woh es tasweer mein hai?
Haan, wo yahan hai, mairay waldain kay paas.
Aur tumharay waldain kya kartay hain?
